Body:
What We've Learned Updated: Post patching, we are still seeing the issue with the Windows Schedule task not running the NEA application yet the task notes that it completed successfully in only 3< seconds.

I suspect CrowdStrike rule update is blocking the task scheduler from fully calling the needed EXE.

Next Steps Updated: Contact will work with his team to confirm the needed Antivirus Exclusions for Netwrix Enterprise Auditor
